{
  "stem": "11642.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Bereishit is the first one which I got to know a little bit more than the others.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I liked to read, in general.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Right now, I'm reading a little bit lighter, but I used to read more history books, because this was in my mind always.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was interested, especially in the heritage, and the life of our forefathers, and forever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How-- how we are raised-- this is the way my parents all wanted-- don't forget who your forefathers were and what's your heritage.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember about my mother being a good looking woman, very stunny, and helping my father a lot in the store.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sharing, I should say, with my father, because my father was the one, in the morning, to check us going out to school, if we dressed proper, if everything is done, if we have our lunches with, what to do in school, how to obey.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother already was busy in the kitchen, and up in the store, and help, out because my father was a lot spending a lot of time in his shul, teaching and always learn more and more.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Poland?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my life, the-- the first-- well, like I said, as a child in the school I remember little things, especially when the-- those holidays came with-- you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war broke out?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1939.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember we start to prepare ourselves with food, of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I remember they said we should leave town and run to another city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They thought the other city's going to be safe which was next to ours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we did so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We closed up everything, and we went to the other city.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
